												DRON KOZMETİĞİ
											</H1>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="row-lg-10" style="height: 80%;">
										<div class="row " style=" display: block; margin: 0;">
											<div class="COSMETICTABLE">
												<div>
													<img src="~/PLAYSCRIBE_Frontend/Images/Drone1.png" class="CELLS">
